# Auto-generated indices (rebuilt by scripts/build-index.mjs on every commit).
# Suppress diff noise in PR review without breaking merges or the CI staleness
# check (`git diff --exit-code` still detects changes under `-diff`).
#
# index.json / search.json: large machine blobs — render as "binary" on GitHub
# (-diff) and mark generated (collapsed + excluded from language stats).
# index.md: small human-readable RFC registry — keep diffable/loadable, just
# flag as generated so PRs collapse it by default.
#
# NOTE: `-diff`, NOT the `binary` macro — `binary` also sets `-merge`, which
# would turn every concurrent index change into a manual merge conflict.
index.json  -diff linguist-generated
search.json -diff linguist-generated
index.md    linguist-generated
